#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*{battlefield}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  \\subsection*{Overview}\n"
"  \\bigskip\n"
"  The Battlefield Expansion introduces the large \\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{Battlefield Board} and two 1~vs.~1 game modes that focus on tactical combat on the Battlefield Board.\n"
"  Neither of these 2 modes uses the \\pagelink{Map}{Map}.\n"
"  They differ in how players build their Unit and Player Decks:\n"
"  \\smallskip\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item In \\textbf{Adventure Mode}, players experience a card-driven Adventure Phase followed by a final Combat.\n"
"      The Adventure Phase replaces the Map exploration from regular games.\n"
"      During this phase, players use Adventure cards to gather Resources, expand their Town, and develop their Heroes, thereby deciding which units to recruit and which card types to include in their Deck.\n"
"    \\item In \\textbf{Skirmish Mode}, players receive pre-constructed Decks and armies, with minimal control over their composition.\n"
"      Players immediately engage in Combat.\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"*{battlefield}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  \\subsection*{概述}\n"
"  \\bigskip\n"
"  战场扩展包引入了大型\\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{战场板}以及两种专注于在战场板上进行战术战斗的1对1游戏模式。%\n"
"  这两种模式都不使用\\pagelink{Map}{地图}。%\n"
"  两者的区别在于玩家如何构建其单位和玩家牌堆：\n"
"  \\smallskip\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item 在\\textbf{冒险模式}中，玩家体验以牌为驱动的冒险阶段，随后进行最终战斗。%\n"
"      冒险阶段取代了常规游戏中的地图探索。%\n"
"      在此阶段中，玩家使用冒险牌来收集资源、扩建城镇并培养英雄，从而决定招募哪些单位以及在牌堆中包含哪些牌的类型。\n"
"    \\item 在\\textbf{遭遇战模式}中，玩家获得预先构建的牌堆和军队，对其组成的控制极为有限。%\n"
"      玩家立即进入战斗。\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:24
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  You can also use the Battlefield Board instead of the Combat Board in other game modes.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  你也可以在其他游戏模式中使用战场板代替战斗板。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\subsection*{Victory Condition}\n"
"  Victory in Adventure and Skirmish is achieved by defeating all enemy units in the final Combat.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\subsection*{胜利条件}\n"
"  在冒险和遭遇战中，通过击败最终战斗中所有敌方单位来获得胜利。\n"
"\n"

