#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:48
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\pagetarget{battlefield card clarifications}{\\subsection*{Rule Ambiguity}}\n"
"  \\textbf{Note:} Both game modes were designed for the \\textbf{Core Game only}.\n"
"  As a result, the official rules do not address many interactions, particularly those involving expansion content.\n"
"  Although these are not official rules, the game developers have provided guidance on these cases:\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item The official rules remove only \\wikilink{abilities/diplomacy}{Diplomacy} and \\wikilink{abilities/logistics}{Logistics} Ability cards, but common sense applies: the developers also recommend removing other Ability cards which provide no benefit in Battlefield modes, like \\wikilink{abilities/ballistics}{Ballistics} or \\wikilink{abilities/pathfinding}{Pathfinding.}\n"
"    \\item In Skirmish Mode, when a card with no Combat value is drawn, both players may mutually agree to discard it and draw a replacement.\n"
"    \\item All cards in the Adventure phase are single-use.\n"
"      Consequently, resource-generating Permanent \\svg[7]{permanent} cards (e.g.,~\\wikilink{artifacts/inexhaustible_cart_of_ore}{Inexhaustible Cart of Ore}) are limited to their bottom \\svg{instant} effect only.\n"
"      However, other Permanent \\svg[7]{permanent} cards (Schools of Magic and War Machines) can be used in the final Combat phase only.\n"
"    \\item Card effects, which instruct you to remove other cards (e.g.,~Expert \\wikilink{abilities/scholar}{Scholar}), may be played during the Adventure phase, applying their effect to your Deck.\n"
"    \\item When a card has both Combat and non-Combat effects (e.g.,~\\wikilink{artifacts/cape_of_velocity}{Cape of Velocity}), you decide whether to use it in the Adventure phase or reserve it for the final Combat.\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\end{multicols}"
msgstr ""
"  \\pagetarget{battlefield card clarifications}{\\subsection*{规则歧义}}\n"
"  \\textbf{注意：}两种游戏模式均专为\\textbf{核心游戏}设计。%\n"
"  因此，官方规则并未涵盖许多互动情况，尤其是涉及扩展内容的情况。%\n"
"  尽管这些并非官方规则，游戏开发者已就这些情况提供了指导：\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item 官方规则仅移除\\wikilink{abilities/diplomacy}{外交}和\\wikilink{abilities/logistics}{后勤}能力牌，但常识同样适用：开发者还建议移除其他在战场模式中没有任何益处的能力牌，如\\wikilink{abilities/ballistics}{弹道学}或\\wikilink{abilities/pathfinding}{寻路}。\n"
"    \\item 在遭遇战模式中，当抽到没有战斗值的牌时，双方玩家可以共同协商将其弃置并抽取替换牌。\n"
"    \\item 冒险阶段的所有牌均为一次性使用。%\n"
"      因此，产生资源的永久\\svg[7]{permanent}牌（例如，~\\wikilink{artifacts/inexhaustible_cart_of_ore}{无尽矿车}）仅限于使用其底部的\\svg{instant}效果。%\n"
"      然而，其他永久\\svg[7]{permanent}牌（魔法学派和战争机器）只能在最终战斗阶段使用。\n"
"    \\item 指示你移除其他牌的卡牌效果（例如，专家\\wikilink{abilities/scholar}{学者}）可以在冒险阶段使用，将其效果应用于你的牌堆。\n"
"    \\item 当一张牌同时具有战斗和非战斗效果时（例如，\\wikilink{artifacts/cape_of_velocity}{迅捷斗篷}），你可以决定是在冒险阶段使用它，还是将其保留到最终战斗。\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\end{multicols}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:72
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*{battlefield}\n"
"  \\subheader{Adventure and Skirmish Setup}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"    \\subsection*{Common Setup Steps \\hspace*{-1.6em}\\raisebox{.2\\height}{\\encirclelegend{goblin}{C}}}\n"
"    \\begin{enumerate}[leftmargin=1.5em]\n"
"      \\item Place the Battlefield Board in the middle of the table.\n"
"      \\item Each player chooses a Faction and a Hero of that Faction and takes the following components:\n"
"      \\begin{itemize}\n"
"        \\item[a)] Hero Board\n"
"        \\item[b)] 3 Hero-specific Specialty cards and 1 Hero-specific Ability card\n"
"        \\item[c)] 7 unit cards and 7 unit miniatures\n"
"        \\item[d)] 20 Faction Cubes\n"
"      \\end{itemize}\n"
"      \\item Prepare the Artifact, Spell, and Ability Decks normally.\n"
"        Remove the following Ability cards from the play: \\wikilink{abilities/diplomacy}{Diplomacy,} \\wikilink{abilities/logistics}{Logistics.}\n"
"      \\item Prepare the Positive and Negative \\pagelink{Morale Cards}{\\textbf{Morale cards}} (including all cards with the battlefield symbol).\n"
"      \\item Prepare the following Tokens near the Battlefield Board: Black Cubes, Damage Tokens, Defense/Paralysis Tokens, Obstacles, and the Initiative Token.\n"
"      \\item Prepare the Attack and Resource Dice.\n"
"      \\item Build your starting Deck as per \\pagelink{SetupStartingDeck}{steps \\ref*{SetupStartingDeck}--\\ref*{SetupStartingDeckEnd} of Setup}.\n"
"    \\end{enumerate}\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"*{battlefield}\n"
"  \\subheader{冒险与遭遇战准备}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"    \\subsection*{通用准备步骤 \\hspace*{-1em}\\raisebox{.2\\height}{\\encirclelegend{goblin}{C}}}\n"
"    \\begin{enumerate}[leftmargin=1.5em]\n"
"      \\item 将战斗板放在桌子中央。\n"
"      \\item 每位玩家选择一个阵营及该阵营的一位英雄，并取得以下组件：\n"
"      \\begin{itemize}\n"
"        \\item[a)] 英雄板\n"
"        \\item[b)] 3张英雄专属特长牌和1张英雄专属能力牌\n"
"        \\item[c)] 7张单位牌和7个单位模型\n"
"        \\item[d)] 20个阵营方块\n"
"      \\end{itemize}\n"
"      \\item 正常准备神器、法术和能力牌堆。%\n"
"        然后从游戏中移除以下能力牌：\\wikilink{abilities/diplomacy}{外交术}，\\wikilink{abilities/logistics}{后勤术}。\n"
"      \\item 准备高昂和低落\\pagelink{Morale Cards}{\\textbf{士气牌}}（包括所有带有战场符号的牌）。\n"
"      \\item 在战斗板旁准备以下标记：黑色方块、伤害标记、防御/麻痹标记、障碍物和先攻标记。\n"
"      \\item 准备攻击骰和资源骰。\n"
"      \\item 按照\\pagelink{SetupStartingDeck}{准备步骤\\ref*{SetupStartingDeck}--\\ref*{SetupStartingDeckEnd}}组建你的初始牌堆。\n"
"    \\end{enumerate}\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:87
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    \\subsection*{Additional Steps for Adventure Mode \\hspace*{-1.6em}\\raisebox{.2\\height}{\\encirclelegend{darkcandyapplered}{A}}}\n"
"    \\begin{enumerate}[leftmargin=1.5em, resume]\n"
"      \\item Prepare Resource Tokens and Treasure Dice.\n"
"      \\item Each player takes a Town Board with the following starting setup:\n"
"      \\begin{itemize}\n"
"        \\item[a)] Set income tracks to 10 \\svg{gold}, 0 \\svg{building_materials}, and 0 \\svg{valuables}.\n"
"        \\item[b)] No Town Buildings or units in the Unit Deck.  % Clarification: https://boardgamegeek.com/thread/3284421/article/44125381#44125381\n"
"      \\end{itemize}\n"
"      \\item Starting resources: 15 \\svg{gold}, 3 \\svg{building_materials}, and 1 \\svg{valuables}.\n"
"      \\item Shuffle the Adventure Deck and place it face down.\n"
"      \\item Place the Round Tracker and put a Black Cube on Round 1.\n"
"      \\item Set Hero Level to I.\n"
"      \\item Set your starting Deck aside for now; you will only need it for the final Combat.\n"
"    \\end{enumerate}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"    \\subsection*{冒险模式的额外步骤 \\hspace*{-1em}\\raisebox{.2\\height}{\\encirclelegend{darkcandyapplered}{A}}}\n"
"    \\begin{enumerate}[leftmargin=1.5em, resume]\n"
"      \\item 准备资源标记和宝物骰。\n"
"      \\item 每位玩家取一块城镇面板，设置如下：\n"
"      \\begin{itemize}\n"
"        \\item[a)] 将收入轨道设置为10\\svg{gold}、0\\svg{building_materials}，以及0\\svg{valuables}。\n"
"        \\item[b)] 城镇中没有城镇建筑，单位牌堆中也没有单位。  % Clarification: https://boardgamegeek.com/thread/3284421/article/44125381#44125381\n"
"      \\end{itemize}\n"
"      \\item 起始资源：15\\svg{gold}、3\\svg{building_materials}，以及1\\svg{valuables}。\n"
"      \\item 洗匀冒险牌堆并正面朝下放置。\n"
"      \\item 放置轮次轨道，并将黑色方块放在第1轮上。\n"
"      \\item 将英雄等级设置为I。\n"
"      \\item 暂时将起始牌堆放在一旁；你只会在最终战斗中需要它。\n"
"    \\end{enumerate}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:92
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    \\subsection*{Start of the game}\n"
"    In both modes, both players roll 2~\\svg{resource_die}.\n"
"    The player with the highest total becomes the first player and takes the Initiative Token.\n"
"\\end{multicols}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"    \\subsection*{游戏开始}\n"
"    在两种模式中，双方玩家各投掷2~\\svg{resource_die}。%\n"
"    总点数最高的玩家成为先手玩家，并取得先手标记。\n"
"\\end{multicols}\n"
"\n"

