#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:167
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*[before=\\vspace*{-11mm}]{battlefield}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Adventure}{\\subheader{Adventure Mode}}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  Adventure Mode is divided into two phases: the \\textbf{Adventure Phase} and the \\textbf{Final Combat}.\n"
"  The latter works identically to Skirmish Mode.\\par\n"
"  Before starting the game, both players choose a game length by setting the number of Rounds in the Adventure Phase:\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Short} game: 9 Rounds.\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Medium} game: 13 Rounds.\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Large} game: 16 Rounds.\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\subsection*{Adventure Phase}\n"
"  The Adventure Phase lasts a certain number of Rounds, depending on the chosen game length.\n"
"  Follow these steps in order during each Round.\\par\n"
"  \\begin{enumerate}[leftmargin=1.3em]\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Move the Round Tracker} -- skip this step in the first Round.\n"
"    Depending on the type of Round, resolve the following effects:\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"      \\item In \\textbf{Resource Rounds} both players gain income normally.\n"
"      \\item In \\textbf{Astrologers Rounds} -- instead of drawing Astrologers Proclaim cards, players increase one of their income tracks (\\svg{gold}, \\svg{building_materials}, or \\svg{valuables}) in one of the following ways:\n"
"      \\begin{itemize}\n"
"        \\item Increase your preferred income track.\n"
"        \\item Determine it randomly by rolling a \\svg{resource_die}.\n"
"          If you do, gain the basic income of that resource immediately, which is 5~\\svg{gold}, 2~\\svg{building_materials}, or 1~\\svg{valuables}.\n"
"      \\end{itemize}\n"
"    \\end{itemize}\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Determine starting player} -- in odd-numbered Rounds, it's the player \\textbf{with} the Initiative Token, in even-numbered Rounds, it's the player \\textbf{without it}.\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Draw Adventure Cards} -- skip this step in the last Round.\n"
"    The starting player draws 3 Adventure cards and takes one of them \\textbf{into their hand}.\n"
"    Afterwards, they pass the remaining 2 to the other player, who takes 1 card into their hand and discards the other.\\par\n"
"    \\textbf{Note:} Before choosing the card, \\textbf{the starting player} may use \\svg{movement} effects from \\pagelink{Adventure MM Cards}{set aside cards from your Deck} to discard any number of the drawn Adventure cards and draw that many cards.\\par\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Player Turns} -- beginning with the starting player, both players take their turn by performing any of the following actions in any order:\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"      \\item \\pagelink{Adventure Cards}{\\textbf{Resolve}} an Adventure card from your hand.\n"
"        You may only resolve \\textbf{one Adventure card per Round}.\n"
"      \\item Perform Town or Morale actions, or resolve your Hero's \\pagelink{Level}{level ups}, in the same way as in regular games.  % no-check-caps\n"
"      \\item Use the effects of \\pagelink{Adventure MM Cards}{set aside cards from your Deck}, except for \\svg{movement}.\n"
"    \\end{itemize}\\par\n"
"    At the end of the turn, \\textbf{discard your hand down to 1 Adventure card}.\n"
"    If you still have a \\textbf{Magic Spring} Adventure card in hand, \\textbf{discard it}.\n"
"  \\end{enumerate}\\par\n"
"  \\smallskip\n"
"  In the last Round, players do not draw Adventure cards, but they may still resolve an Adventure card from their hand.\n"
"  After the last Round, the Adventure Phase ends and the final Combat begins.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"*[before=\\vspace*{-11mm}]{battlefield}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Adventure}{\\subheader{冒险模式}}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  冒险模式分为两个阶段：\\textbf{冒险阶段}和\\textbf{最终战斗}。%\n"
"  后者与遭遇战模式完全相同。\\par\n"
"  在游戏开始前，两位玩家通过设定冒险阶段的轮次数来选择游戏时长：\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{短}局游戏：9轮。\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{中}局游戏：13轮。\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{长}局游戏：16轮。\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\subsection*{冒险阶段}\n"
"  冒险阶段持续一定数量的轮次，具体取决于所选的游戏时长。%\n"
"  在每轮中，按顺序执行以下步骤。\\par\n"
"  \\begin{enumerate}[leftmargin=1.3em]\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{移动轮次轨道} -- 第一轮跳过此步骤。%\n"
"    根据轮次类型，执行以下效果：\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"      \\item \\mbox{在\\textbf{资源轮}中，两位玩家正常获得收入。}\n"
"      \\item 在\\textbf{星相家轮}中 -- 玩家不是抽取星相家宣告牌，而是以下列方式之一提升其中一条收入轨道（\\svg{gold}、\\svg{building_materials}或\\svg{valuables}）：\n"
"      \\begin{itemize}\n"
"        \\item 提升你偏好的收入轨道。\n"
"        \\item 通过投掷\\svg{resource_die}随机决定。%\n"
"          若如此，立即获得该资源的基础收入，即5\\svg{gold}、2\\svg{building_materials}或1\\svg{valuables}。\n"
"      \\end{itemize}\n"
"    \\end{itemize}\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{确定先手玩家} -- 在奇数轮，先手玩家是\\textbf{持有}先手标记的玩家；在偶数轮，先手玩家是\\textbf{未持有}先手标记的玩家。\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{抽取冒险牌} -- 最后一轮跳过此步骤。%\n"
"    先手玩家抽取3张冒险牌，并将其中一张\\textbf{加入手中}。%\n"
"    之后，将剩余2张传给另一位玩家，后者将其中1张加入手中并弃置另一张。\\par\n"
"    \\textbf{注意：}在选牌之前，\\textbf{先手玩家}可以使用\\pagelink{Adventure MM Cards}{从你的牌堆中搁置的牌}的\\svg{movement}效果，弃置任意数量已抽取的冒险牌，并抽取相同数量的牌。\\par\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{玩家回合} -- 从先手玩家开始，两位玩家以任意顺序执行以下任意行动：\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"      \\item \\pagelink{Adventure Cards}{\\textbf{结算}}你手中的一张冒险牌。%\n"
"        每轮只能结算\\textbf{一张冒险牌}。\n"
"      \\item 执行城镇或士气行动，或结算你英雄的\\pagelink{Level}{升级}，方式与常规游戏相同。  % no-check-caps\n"
"      \\item 使用\\pagelink{Adventure MM Cards}{从你的牌堆中搁置的牌}的效果，\\svg{movement}效果除外。\n"
"    \\end{itemize}\\par\n"
"    在回合结束时，\\textbf{弃置手牌至仅剩1张冒险牌}。%\n"
"    若你手中仍有\\textbf{魔法泉}冒险牌，\\mbox{\\textbf{弃置它}。}\n"
"  \\end{enumerate}\\par\n"
"  \\smallskip\n"
"  在最后一轮，玩家不抽取冒险牌，但仍可结算手中的冒险牌。%\n"
"  最后一轮结束后，冒险阶段结束，最终战斗开始。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:173
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\subsection*{Starting the final Combat}\n"
"  Recover all spent \\svg{expert}.\n"
"  Pick up your Deck, shuffle it, and draw cards up to your Hero's Hand \\svg{hand} Limit.\n"
"  Remove all \\svg{paralysis} tokens from your units, take all your unit Miniatures, and begin the final Combat on the Battlefield Board following the \\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{Battlefield Combat rules}.\n"
"  \\end{multicols}"
msgstr ""
"  \\subsection*{开始最终战斗}\n"
"  收回所有已使用的\\svg{expert}。%\n"
"  拿起你的牌堆，洗牌，并抽牌至你的英雄的手牌\\svg{hand}上限。%\n"
"  移除你的单位上的所有\\svg{paralysis}标记，拿走你所有的单位模型，并在战场板上开始最终战斗，遵循\\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{战场战斗规则}。\n"
"  \\end{multicols}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:184
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*{battlefield}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Adventure Cards}{\\subsection*{Resolving Adventure Cards}}\n"
"  There are two types of Adventure cards: Combat and Event.\n"
"  \\medskip\n"
"  \\begin{multicols*}{2}\n"
"    \\footnotesize\n"
