"      \\begin{tikzpicture}\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:237
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"        \\node (card) [inner sep=0] {\\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\cards/adventure_combat.png}};\n"
"        \\begin{relcoords}{card}\n"
"          \\draw (0.7, 0.85) node {\\encirclesmall{1}};\n"
"          \\draw (0.62, 0.5) node {\\encirclesmall{2}};\n"
"          \\draw (0.2, 0.34) node {\\encirclesmall{4}};\n"
"          \\draw (0.8, 0.34) node {\\encirclesmall{5}};\n"
"          \\draw (0.6, 0.08) node {\\encirclesmall{6}};\n"
"        \\end{relcoords}\n"
"      \\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"      \\imagecaption{Adventure-Combat card}\\index{Combat cards (Adventure)}\n"
"      \\begin{enumerate}\n"
"        \\item[\\textbf{4.}] Combat Power Levels\n"
"        \\item[\\textbf{5.}] Battle Reward\n"
"        \\item[\\textbf{6.}] Basic Reward\n"
"      \\end{enumerate}\n"
"    \\end{center}\n"
"  \\end{multicols*}\n"
"  To resolve an \\textbf{Adventure-Event card}, follow its printed effect.\n"
"  To resolve an \\textbf{Adventure-Combat card}, follow these steps:\n"
"  \\begin{enumerate}[leftmargin=1.3em]\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Declare a Combat Power Level:}\\index{Combat Power (Adventure)}\n"
"      Choose one of the three available Combat Power Levels.\n"
"      You must reach at least that value to gain the full reward.\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Determine your Combat Power:}\n"
"      Select 2 of your units and roll 1 Attack Die for each.\n"
"      If you have fewer than 2 units, select as many as you have.\n"
"      Sum all unit Attack values and all Attack Die results to determine your final Combat Power.\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Get the Reward:}\n"
"      If your Combat Power is equal to or higher than your declared Combat Power Level, take both the Basic Reward and the Battle Reward.\n"
"      Otherwise, take only the Basic Reward and place a \\svg{paralysis} token on one of your units that took part in this Combat.\n"
"      This unit is now stunned.\n"
"      If you choose a stunned unit for a future Combat, do not add its Attack value to your Combat Power; then remove the \\svg{paralysis} token from that unit.\n"
"  \\end{enumerate}\n"
"  \\columnbreak\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"        \\node (card) [inner sep=0] {\\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\cards/adventure_combat.png}};\n"
"        \\begin{relcoords}{card}\n"
"          \\draw (0.7, 0.85) node {\\encirclesmall{1}};\n"
"          \\draw (0.62, 0.5) node {\\encirclesmall{2}};\n"
"          \\draw (0.2, 0.34) node {\\encirclesmall{4}};\n"
"          \\draw (0.8, 0.34) node {\\encirclesmall{5}};\n"
"          \\draw (0.6, 0.08) node {\\encirclesmall{6}};\n"
"        \\end{relcoords}\n"
"      \\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"      \\imagecaption{冒险-战斗牌}\\index{战斗牌（冒险）}\n"
"      \\begin{enumerate}\n"
"        \\item[\\textbf{4.}] 战力等级\n"
"        \\item[\\textbf{5.}] 战斗奖励\n"
"        \\item[\\textbf{6.}] 基础奖励\n"
"      \\end{enumerate}\n"
"    \\end{center}\n"
"  \\end{multicols*}\n"
"  处理一张\\textbf{冒险-事件牌}时，遵循其上印刷的效果。\n"
"  处理一张\\textbf{冒险-战斗牌}时，遵循以下步骤：\n"
"  \\begin{enumerate}[leftmargin=1.3em]\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{宣告战力等级：}\\index{战斗力（冒险）}%\n"
"      从三个可用的战力等级中选择一个。%\n"
"      你必须达到至少该数值，才能获得完整奖励。\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{确定你的战斗力：}%\n"
"      选择你的2个单位，为每个单位掷1个攻击骰。%\n"
"      如果你的单位少于2个，选择你拥有的所有单位。%\n"
"      将所有单位的攻击值与所有攻击骰结果相加，以确定你的最终战斗力。\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{获得奖励：}%\n"
"      如果你的战斗力等于或高于你所宣告的战力等级，则同时获得基础奖励和战斗奖励。%\n"
"      否则，只获得基础奖励，并在参与此次战斗的一个单位上放置一个\\svg{paralysis}标记。%\n"
"      该单位现在处于眩晕状态。%\n"
"      如果你在未来的战斗中选择了一个眩晕单位，不将其攻击值计入你的战斗力；然后从该单位上移除\\svg{paralysis}标记。\n"
"  \\end{enumerate}\n"
"  \\columnbreak\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:240
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  After resolving an Adventure card, place it in \\textbf{your own} pile of resolved cards.\n"
"  For example, the Adventure-Event card ``Obelisk'' grows stronger with each Obelisk card you have played previously.\\par\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  在结算一张冒险牌后，将其放入\\textbf{你自己的}已结算牌堆。%\n"
"  例如，冒险-事件牌“方尖碑”会随着你此前每打出一张方尖碑牌而变得更强。\\par\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:261
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\pagetarget{Adventure MM Cards}{\\subsection*{Managing Your Deck in Adventure Mode}}\n"
"  Your Deck is not available during the Adventure Phase.\n"
"  Instead, the following rules apply:\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item Place all cards of your starting Deck face down near your Hero Board.\n"
"      They will be used in the final Combat.\n"
"    \\item Your \\svg{expert} limit applies to the entire Adventure Phase.\n"
"      Recover all spent \\svg{expert} at the start of the final Combat.\n"
"    \\item Each time an effect instructs you to gain new cards (usually from leveling up or resolving Adventure cards), proceed as follows:\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"      \\item Cards that are \\textbf{useful only in Combat} go directly into your Deck and remain there until the final Combat.\n"
"        You can't use these cards during Adventure Phase.\n"
"        Spells always go into your Deck, since their alternative effect (+1~\\svg{empower}) is always useful in Combat.\n"
"      \\item Cards that \\textbf{are not useful in Combat} because they provide Resources (e.g., \\wikilink{abilities/estates}{Estates}) or \\svg{movement}, or provide discounts (e.g., \\wikilink{artifacts/legs_of_legion}{Legs of Legion,} \\wikilink{abilities/wisdom}{Wisdom}), are \\textbf{set aside} next to your Hero Board.\n"
"        Each of these cards may be used \\textbf{once, then removed} from the game.\n"
"        These cards do not go into your Deck.\n"
"      \\item If you are unsure how to categorize a card, note that clear rules do not exist for every individual case, and you may need to follow \\pagelink{battlefield card clarifications}{game developers' clarifications}, or agree on a house rule with your opponent.\n"
"    \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\end{multicols}"
msgstr ""
"  \\pagetarget{Adventure MM Cards}{\\subsection*{在冒险模式中管理你的牌堆}}\n"
"  你的牌堆在冒险阶段不可用。%\n"
"  取而代之，以下规则适用：\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item 将你起始牌堆中的所有牌面朝下放置在你的英雄板附近。%\n"
"      它们将在最终战斗中使用。\n"
"    \\item 你的\\svg{expert}上限适用于整个冒险阶段。%\n"
"      在最终战斗开始时，恢复所有已使用的\\svg{expert}。\n"
"    \\item 每当效果指示你获得新牌（通常来自等级提升或解决冒险牌），按以下方式处理：\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"      \\item \\textbf{仅在战斗中有用}的牌直接进入你的牌堆，并留在那里直到最终战斗。%\n"
"        你在冒险阶段不能使用这些牌。%\n"
"        法术总是进入你的牌堆，因为它们的替代效果（+1~\\svg{empower}）在战斗中总是有用的。\n"
"      \\item \\textbf{在战斗中无用}的牌，因为它们提供资源（例如，\\wikilink{abilities/estates}{庄园}）或\\svg{movement}，或提供折扣（例如，\\wikilink{artifacts/legs_of_legion}{兵团之腿}，\\wikilink{abilities/wisdom}{智慧}），会被\\textbf{搁置}在你的英雄板旁边。%\n"
"        这些牌每张可以使用\\textbf{一次，然后从游戏中移除}。%\n"
"        这些牌不会进入你的牌堆。\n"
"      \\item 如果你不确定如何对一张牌进行分类，请注意并非每种情况都有明确的规则，你可能需要遵循\\pagelink{battlefield card clarifications}{游戏开发者的说明}，或与对手商定一个自定规则。\n"
"    \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"  \\end{multicols}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:273
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*{battlefield}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Skirmish}{\\subheader{Skirmish Mode}}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"    Skirmish Mode has no Adventure Phase.\n"
"    Skip that phase, prepare your Deck, and proceed directly to the final Combat.\\par\n"
"    \\vspace*{1em}\n"
"    \\subsection*{Deck Preparation}\n"
"    Both players decide on a game length: \\textbf{short, medium, or large}.\n"
"    Depending on the chosen game length, both players modify their Hero's Level, their Deck (by drawing additional cards), and their Unit Deck as shown in the table below.\\par\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"*{battlefield}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Skirmish}{\\subheader{遭遇战模式}}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"    遭遇战模式没有冒险阶段。%\n"
"    跳过该阶段，准备你的牌堆，并直接进行最终战斗。\\par\n"
"    \\vspace*{1em}\n"
"    \\subsection*{牌堆准备}\n"
"    两位玩家决定游戏时长：\\textbf{短、中或长}。%\n"
"    根据所选游戏时长，两位玩家按下表修改其英雄的等级、牌堆（通过抽取额外牌）以及单位牌堆。\\par\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:279
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    \\vspace*{1em}\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"    \\subsection*{Starting the final Combat}\n"
"    After modifying your Deck, shuffle it and draw cards up to your Hand Limit.\n"
"    Then follow the rules for \\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{Combat on the Battlefield Board}.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"    \\vspace*{1em}\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"    \\subsection*{开始最终战斗}\n"
"    修改你的牌堆后，将其洗牌并抽牌至手牌上限。%\n"
"    然后遵循\\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{战场板上的战斗}的规则。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:282
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
