#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:326
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*[before=\\vspace*{-11mm}]{battlefield}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Battlefield Combat}{\\subheader{Battlefield Combat}}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols*}{2}\n"
"  Playing on the Battlefield Board requires using Miniatures for Combat instead of unit cards.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"*[before=\\vspace*{-11mm}]{battlefield}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Battlefield Combat}{\\subheader{战场战斗}}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols*}{2}\n"
"  在战场板上进行游戏需要使用微缩模型进行战斗，而不是单位牌。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:354
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\subsection*{\\pagetarget{BF Obstacles}{Obstacle Tokens}}\n"
"  You can place three token types on the Battlefield Board: Effect, Obstacle and Wall/\\allowbreak Gate.\n"
"  Unless otherwise stated, these Tokens count and work as \\pagelink{Combatterminology}{Combat Obstacles}.\n"
"  To place Effect Obstacles on the Battlefield Board you'll need the card that creates the effect, such as the \\wikilink{spells/fire_wall}{Fire Wall} Spell: use the Tokens and put the card beside the Battlefield as a reminder.\n"
"  Effect Obstacles may be entered by units, if the card text allows it.\n"
"  \\begin{figure}[H]\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\begin{subfigure}[b]{0.3\\linewidth}\n"
"      \\centering\n"
"      \\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\images/bf-obstacle-1.png}\n"
"      \\caption{\\imagecaption{Effect}}\n"
"    \\end{subfigure}\n"
"    \\begin{subfigure}[b]{0.3\\linewidth}\n"
"      \\centering\n"
"      \\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\images/bf-obstacle-2.png}\n"
"      \\caption{\\imagecaption{Obstacle}}\n"
"    \\end{subfigure}\n"
"    \\begin{subfigure}[b]{0.3\\linewidth}\n"
"      \\centering\n"
"      \\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\images/bf-obstacle-3.png}\n"
"      \\caption{\\imagecaption{Wall/Gate}}\n"
"    \\end{subfigure}\n"
"  \\end{figure}\n"
"  \\vspace*{-0.5\\baselineskip}\n"
"  \\note{3}{\n"
"    All unit Miniatures also count as Obstacles.\n"
"  }\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\subsection*{\\pagetarget{BF Obstacles}{障碍标记}}\n"
"  你可以在战场板上放置三种类型的标记：效果、障碍和城墙/\\allowbreak 城门。%\n"
"  除非另有说明，这些标记计为并作为\\pagelink{Combatterminology}{战斗障碍}。%\n"
"  要在战场板上放置效果障碍，你需要创建该效果的牌，例如\\wikilink{spells/fire_wall}{火墙}法术牌：使用这些标记并将牌放在战场旁边作为提醒。%\n"
"  效果障碍可被单位进入，若牌面文字允许。\n"
"  \\begin{figure}[H]\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\begin{subfigure}[b]{0.3\\linewidth}\n"
"      \\centering\n"
"      \\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\images/bf-obstacle-1.png}\n"
"      \\caption{\\imagecaption{效果}}\n"
"    \\end{subfigure}\n"
"    \\begin{subfigure}[b]{0.3\\linewidth}\n"
"      \\centering\n"
"      \\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\images/bf-obstacle-2.png}\n"
"      \\caption{\\imagecaption{障碍}}\n"
"    \\end{subfigure}\n"
"    \\begin{subfigure}[b]{0.3\\linewidth}\n"
"      \\centering\n"
"      \\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\images/bf-obstacle-3.png}\n"
"      \\caption{\\imagecaption{城墙/城门}}\n"
"    \\end{subfigure}\n"
"  \\end{figure}\n"
"  \\vspace*{-0.5\\baselineskip}\n"
"  \\note{3}{\n"
"    所有单位模型也计为障碍。\n"
"  }\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:367
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\vspace*{-1em}\n"
"  \\subsection*{Combat Setup}\n"
"  \\setlength\\intextsep{0pt}\n"
"  \\setlength\\columnsep{1em}\n"
"  \\begin{wrapfigure}{r}{0.33\\linewidth}\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\images/initiative-bf.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\caption{\\imagecaption[c]{\\mbox{Initiative} Token}}\n"
"    \\vspace{1em}\n"
"  \\end{wrapfigure}\n"
"  Starting with the player with the \\pagetarget{Initiative Token}{\\textbf{Initiative Token}}\\index{Initiative Token} (the attacker in a \\pagelinkwithcomma{BF for regular}{non-Adventure/Skirmish game}), both players take turns choosing and placing Obstacle Tokens on the Battlefield Board one-by-one until \\textbf{all Obstacle Tokens (except Effects) are placed}.\n"
"  No Obstacle can be adjacent to another Obstacle or to any player's deployment zone.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\vspace*{-1em}\n"
"  \\subsection*{战斗准备}\n"
"  \\setlength\\intextsep{0pt}\n"
"  \\setlength\\columnsep{1em}\n"
"  \\begin{wrapfigure}{r}{0.33\\linewidth}\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\images/initiative-bf.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\caption{\\imagecaption[c]{\\mbox{先攻}标记}}\n"
"    \\vspace{1em}\n"
"  \\end{wrapfigure}\n"
"  从拥有\\pagetarget{Initiative Token}{\\textbf{先攻标记}}\\index{先攻标记}的玩家（在\\pagelinkwithcomma{BF for regular}{非冒险/遭遇战游戏}中的攻击方）开始，双方玩家轮流选择并将障碍标记逐一放置在战场板上，直到\\textbf{所有障碍标记（效果除外）均已放置}。%\n"
"  任何障碍标记不能与其他障碍标记或任何玩家的部署区相邻。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:381
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  {\\centering\n"
"    \\begin{tikzpicture}\n"
"      \\draw (0, 0) node {\\framedimage[\\linewidth]{\\examples/bf-deploy.png}};\n"
"      \\draw (3.2, 0) node[rotate=90, fill=black, fill opacity=0.19, text opacity=1]\n"
"        {\\textbf{\\liberation\\LARGE\\textcolor{white}{\\MakeUppercase{Deployment Zone}}}};\n"
"    \\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"  }\\\\\n"
"  \\imagecaption{Obstacles and Miniatures placed correctly are marked with the green border, and incorrectly -- with the red one.}\\par\n"
"  \\vspace{1em}\n"
"    The player with the Initiative Token chooses a deployment zone and places one of their units in it, then players take turns placing their units \\textbf{one by one} each in their zone.\n"
"    The 5-unit limit does not apply in Adventure and Skirmish modes, and players may place all Faction units available to them.\n"
"    When the last unit is placed, the Combat begins.\n"
"  \\end{multicols*}"
msgstr ""
"  {\\centering\n"
"    \\begin{tikzpicture}\n"
"      \\draw (0, 0) node {\\framedimage[\\linewidth]{\\examples/bf-deploy.png}};\n"
"      \\draw (3.2, 0) node[rotate=90, fill=black, fill opacity=0.19, text opacity=1]\n"
"        {\\textbf{\\liberation\\LARGE\\textcolor{white}{\\MakeUppercase{部署区域}}}};\n"
"    \\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"  }\\\\\n"
"  \\imagecaption{放置正确的障碍物和模型用绿色边框标记，放置不正确的则用红色边框标记。}\\par\n"
"  \\vspace{1em}\n"
"    持有先攻标记的玩家选择一个部署区域，并在其中放置一个己方单位，然后玩家轮流在各自区域内\\textbf{逐一}放置单位。%\n"
"    5单位限制在冒险模式和遭遇战模式中不适用，玩家可以放置所有可用的阵营单位。%\n"
"    当最后一个单位放置完毕后，战斗开始。\n"
"  \\end{multicols*}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:393
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*[before=\\vspace*{-11mm}]{battlefield}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols*}{2}\n"
"  \\subsection*{Battlefield Combat Rules}\n"
"  Follow the regular \\pagelink{combatround}{Combat rules} with the following changes:\n"
"  \\bigbreak\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Unit Movement} -- Each unit's Movement is equal to its Initiative value: a unit of Initiative 8 can move up to 8 hexes.\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Ranged Movement} -- Ranged \\svg{unit_ranged} units can either move or attack, not both.\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{Combat Penalty} -- Ranged \\svg{unit_ranged} units suffer a Combat Penalty when attacking an adjacent unit or a unit that is \\textbf{8 or more} hexes away from them.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"*[before=\\vspace*{-11mm}]{battlefield}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols*}{2}\n"
"  \\subsection*{战场战斗规则}\n"
"  遵循常规\\pagelink{combatround}{战斗规则}，并做以下修改：\n"
"  \\bigbreak\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{单位移动} -- 每个单位的移动力等于其先攻值：先攻值为8的单位最多可移动8格。\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{远程移动} -- 远程\\svg{unit_ranged}单位只能移动或攻击，两者不可兼得。\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{战斗惩罚} -- 远程\\svg{unit_ranged}单位在攻击相邻单位或距离其\\textbf{8格或更远}的单位时，会受到战斗惩罚。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:397
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    \\item \\textbf{Initiative Tie} -- If two or more opposing units have the same Initiative value, the player with the \\textbf{Initiative Token} activates one of their units first.\n"
"      Then, the players alternate in activating all of their units of that same Initiative value one by one.\n"
"      Once all units with that Initiative value were activated, pass the Initiative Token to the other player, who keeps it until an Initiative tie of opposing units happens again.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"    \\item \\textbf{先攻平局} -- 若两个或更多对方单位拥有相同的先攻值，持有\\textbf{先攻标记}的玩家先激活其中一个单位。%\n"
"      然后，玩家们轮流逐个激活各自所有拥有该先攻值的单位。%\n"
"      一旦所有拥有该先攻值的单位均被激活，将先攻标记传给另一位玩家，该玩家持有先攻标记，直到对方单位再次发生先攻平局为止。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:400
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    \\item \\textbf{In \\pagelink{Adventure and Skirmish Modes}{Adventure and Skirmish} only} -- At the end of each Combat Round, \\textbf{regain one used \\svg{expert}} up to your Hero's Limit, and \\textbf{draw 2 cards from your Deck}.\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"    \\item \\textbf{仅在\\pagelink{Adventure and Skirmish Modes}{冒险和遭遇战}中} -- 在每个战斗轮次结束时，\\textbf{恢复一个已使用的\\svg{expert}}（不超过你的英雄上限），并\\textbf{从你的牌堆中摸2张牌}。\n"
"  \\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/battlefield.tex:402 sections/deckbuilding.tex:65
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:407
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\begin{center}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=1.05\\linewidth]{\\art/dendroid.jpg}\n"
"  \\end{center}\n"
"  \\end{multicols*}"
msgstr ""
"  \\begin{center}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=1.05\\linewidth]{\\art/dendroid.jpg}\n"
"  \\end{center}\n"
"  \\end{multicols*}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:413
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*[before=\\vspace*{-11mm}]{battlefield}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{BF for regular}{\\subheader{Battlefield Board in regular games}}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols*}{2}\n"
"    Although Battlefield is designed for \\pagelink{Adventure and Skirmish Modes}{Adventure and Skirmish modes}, it is possible to use the Battlefield Board in other game modes, though with minor rule modifications.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"*[before=\\vspace*{-11mm}]{battlefield}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{BF for regular}{\\subheader{常规游戏中的战场板}}\n"
"  \\begin{multicols*}{2}\n"
"    虽然战场是为\\pagelink{Adventure and Skirmish Modes}{冒险模式和遭遇战模式}设计的，但也可以在其他游戏模式中使用战场板，只需进行少量规则修改。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:415
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    \\subsection*{Changes to Combat Rules}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"    \\subsection*{战斗规则变更}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:422
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"      \\item The attacker receives the Initiative Token at the start of the Combat Setup.\n"
"      \\item In player vs. player Combat, you may place up to 7 units.\n"
"        In Neutral Combat, the 5-unit limit still applies.\n"
"      \\item Playing on the Battlefield Board requires using rules for \\pagelink{Miniatures}{Miniatures}.\n"
"    \\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"      \\item \\mbox{攻击方在战斗准备开始时获得先攻标记。}\n"
"      \\item 在玩家对玩家的战斗中，你最多可以放置7个单位。%\n"
"        在中立战斗中，5单位上限仍然适用。\n"
"      \\item \\mbox{在战场板上游戏需要使用\\pagelink{Miniatures}{模型}的规则。}\n"
"    \\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:427
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    \\subsection*{Siege with Walls and Gate}\n"
"    During a Siege against a Town with a Citadel\\index{Citadel}, Walls and Gate Obstacles are placed as shown below.\n"
"    Place no other Obstacles.\\par\n"
"    \\bigskip\n"
"    \\begin{tikzpicture}\n"
msgstr ""
"    \\subsection*{带城墙和城门的围城战}\n"
"    在围攻拥有大本营\\index{大本营}的城镇时，城墙和城门障碍物按下图所示放置。%\n"
"    不放置其他障碍物。\\par\n"
"    \\bigskip\n"
"    \\begin{tikzpicture}\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:434
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"      \\draw (0, 0) node {\\framedimage[\\linewidth]{\\examples/bf-deploy-wall.png}};\n"
"      \\draw (2.5, 0) node[rotate=90, fill=black, fill opacity=0.15, text opacity=1]\n"
"        {\\textbf{\\liberation\\LARGE\\textcolor{white}{\\MakeUppercase{Deployment Zone}}}};\n"
"    \\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"    \\imagecaption{The red border marks incorrectly placed Obstacles.}\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"      \\draw (0, 0) node {\\framedimage[\\linewidth]{\\examples/bf-deploy-wall.png}};\n"
"      \\draw (2.5, 0) node[rotate=90, fill=black, fill opacity=0.15, text opacity=1]\n"
"        {\\textbf{\\liberation\\LARGE\\textcolor{white}{\\MakeUppercase{部署区域}}}};\n"
"    \\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"    \\imagecaption{红色边框标记了放置不正确的障碍物。}\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:440
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    During a Siege, defending units may enter the Gate Token \\textbf{only through the two middle hexes} where the Gate is printed.\n"
"    Attacking the Gate Token is still possible on all four hexes.\\par\n"
"    \\bigskip\n"
"    \\framedimage[\\linewidth]{\\examples/bf-gate-token.png}\n"
"    \\textit{\\footnotesize{}Example: Halberdier and Crusader (defenders) may enter the Gate Token only along the green arrows, but Minotaur and Harpy are still able to attack the Gate Token from any side.}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"    在攻城战中，防御单位\\textbf{只能通过城门所在的中间两格}进入城门标记。%\n"
"    从所有四格攻击城门标记仍然可行。\\par\n"
"    \\bigskip\n"
"    \\framedimage[\\linewidth]{\\examples/bf-gate-token.png}\n"
"    \\textit{\\footnotesize{}示例：戟兵和十字军（防御方）只能沿绿色箭头进入城门标记，但牛头人和鸟妖仍能从任意一侧攻击城门标记。}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/battlefield.tex:446
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    \\subsection*{Combat with Neutral Units}\n"
"    If you decide to use the Battlefield Board in Combats with Neutral Units, ignore the Round Limit: at the end of each Combat Round you may freely decide to Retreat or to start another Combat Round with no need to spend \\svg{movement}.\n"
"    Be aware, however, that this may significantly extend the playtime.\n"
"    It is recommended to use the Battlefield Board only for \\textbf{Player vs.~Player Combats}.\n"
"  \\end{multicols*}"
msgstr ""
"    \\subsection*{与中立单位的战斗}\n"
"    如果你决定在与中立单位的战斗中使用战场板，请忽略轮次限制：在每个战斗轮次结束时，你可以自由决定撤退或开始另一个战斗轮次，无需花费\\svg{movement}。%\n"
"    但请注意，这可能会大幅延长游戏时间。%\n"
"    建议仅在\\textbf{玩家对玩家战斗}中使用战场板。\n"
"  \\end{multicols*}"
